nxiety and exploration between the experimental groups, as measured by the percentage of time spent in the center (Figure 6b, inset; one way ANOVA F(3,28)β€�=β€�0.47, p>0.05).10.1371/journal.pbio.1001627.g006Figure 6MPEP eliminates a perseverative behavior in TSC2+/β�’ mice.(a) During reversal training, TSC2+/β�’ mice make significantly more errors toward the conditioned arm in the RAWM (two-way ANOVA; WT nβ€�=β€�21; TSC2 nβ€�=β€�23; F(3, 43)β€�=β€�9.160, pβ€�=β€�0.0034). Differences between individual groups were assessed with paired Mann Whitney t test: Trial 1, WT versus TSC2; pβ€�=β€�0.049. Trial 2, WT versus TSC2, pβ€�=β€�0.010; TSC2 versus TSC2+MPEP; pβ€�=β€�0.0466. (b) There were no differences for open field performance between genotypes (WT nβ€�=β€�14; TSC2 nβ€�=β€�12; TSC2+MPEP nβ€�=β€�14). There were no differences for open pool performance between genotypes. (WT nβ€�=β€�13; TSC2 nβ€�=β€�12; TSC+MPEP nβ€�=β€�14). NS, not significant, *p<0.05, **p<0.005.
